  <brief_title>To Assess Efficacy of Epiitalis on Knee Pain in Patients Suffering From Knee Osteoarthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double Blind, Double Dummy, Dose Response, Randomized, Placebo Controlled Study to Assess the Efficacy of Epiitalis on Knee Pain in Patients Suffering From Knee Osteoarthritis</official_title>
