  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Epiitalis is an ingredient of a currently marketed product named as Osteo-Restore, indicated
      for joint health.The present study is primarily planned to establish the role of Epiitalis as
      a single ingredient in the treatment of mild to moderate cases of knee Osteoarthritis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
